<title>Other Grid functions</title>
<p>
In addition to <c>draw</c> and <c>paint</c>, the <c>GridCanvas</c> class provides functions for working with the grid itself.
<c>numRows</c> and <c>numCols</c> return the number of rows and columns.
We can get this information from the 2D array, using <c>length</c>:
</p>

<program xml:id="arrays-arrays_other-grid-functions-1">
